# Production base path for static hosting (must start and end with `/`).
# Use for GitHub Pages **project** sites: https://username.github.io/repo-name/
# Example: VITE_BASE=/portfolio/
VITE_BASE=/

# For GitHub Pages without Actions, the repo includes `.env.gh-pages` and:
#   npm run deploy:gh-pages
# (build uses `--mode gh-pages` which loads that file).
